```{r setup, include=FALSE}
knitr::opts_chunk$set(echo = TRUE)
library(readxl)
library(ggplot2)
```

```{r}
data <- read_excel("CogER.xlsx")
View(data)
```

```{r}
vis <- ggplot(data, aes(x = Group, y = Score))+
  geom_boxplot()

vis
```

```{r}
one.way <- aov(Score ~ Group, data = data)

summary(one.way)
```
